==English==
===Etymology===
[[a-]] + [[theism]]

===Noun===
'''atheism'''

#the absence of belief in [[deity|deities]]. (weak atheism)
#the claim that no deities exists. (strong atheism)
#the antonym of theism (belief in a [[god]] or gods).

